snippet.title: WORLD BOSS 1.0 - Official Launch Trailer - 1.0 Out Now!
snippet.description:
The game has changed. 

Fresh and LazarBeam present World Boss 1.0.

- Nonstop frenetic FPS mayhem
- Brand new arena
- Unlock perks and master your weapons for millions of builds
- Claim the World Boss title
- Destroy the map with the Corruption Bomb

World Boss is FREE on Steam: https://bit.ly/3MIbyFI 

#worldboss #fpsgame #onlinegame #freetoplay #pcgame

---

World Boss is available now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1628620/World_Boss/ 
Join the World Boss Discord for the latest info, gaming tips and more: https://discord.gg/worldboss
